{"id":899,"parent_id":890,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":899,"title":"Hosea 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hosea","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","The people of Israel are taken into captivity for their sins—Ephraim will be a wanderer among the nations."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.1","order":"02.29.009.60429"},["b","1"],"Rejoice not, O Israel, for joy, as",["i","other"],"people: for thou hast gone a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"whoring"],"from thy God, thou hast loved a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"reward"],"upon every",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"cornfloor"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.2","order":"02.29.009.60430"},["b","2"],"The floor and the winepress shall not feed them, and the new wine shall fail in her."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.3","order":"02.29.009.60431"},["b","3"],"They shall not dwell in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"land"],"; but Ephraim shall return to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Egypt"],", and they shall eat",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"unclean",["i","things"]],"in Assyria."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.4","order":"02.29.009.60432"},["b","4"],"They shall not offer wine",["i","offerings"],"to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", neither shall they be pleasing unto him: their sacrifices",["i","shall be"],"unto them as the bread of mourners; all that eat thereof shall be polluted: for their bread for their soul shall not come into the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.5","order":"02.29.009.60433"},["b","5"],"What will ye do in the solemn day, and in the day of the feast of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.6","order":"02.29.009.60434"},["b","6"],"For, lo, they are gone because of destruction: Egypt shall gather them up, Memphis shall bury them: the pleasant",["i","places"],"for their silver, nettles shall possess them: thorns",["i","shall be"],"in their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"tabernacles"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.7","order":"02.29.009.60435"},["b","7"],"The days of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"visitation"],"are come, the days of recompence are come; Israel shall know",["i","it:"],"the prophet",["i","is"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"fool"],", the spiritual man",["i","is"],"mad, for the multitude of thine iniquity, and the great hatred."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.8","order":"02.29.009.60436"},["b","8"],"The watchman of Ephraim",["i","was"],"with my God:",["i","but"],"the prophet",["i","is"],"a snare of a fowler in all his ways,",["i","and"],"hatred in the house of his God."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.9","order":"02.29.009.60437"},["b","9"],"They have deeply",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"corrupted"],["i","themselves,"],"as in the days of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Gibeah"],":",["i","therefore"],"he will remember their iniquity, he will visit their sins."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.10","order":"02.29.009.60438"},["b","10"],"I found Israel like grapes in the wilderness; I saw your fathers as the firstripe in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"fig tree"],"at her first time:",["i","but"],"they went to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"Baal-peor"],", and separated themselves unto",["i","that"],"shame; and",["i","their"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"abominations"],"were according as they loved."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.11","order":"02.29.009.60439"},["b","11"],["i","As for"],"Ephraim, their glory shall fly away like a bird, from the birth, and from the womb, and from the conception."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.12","order":"02.29.009.60440"},["b","12"],"Though they bring up their children, yet will I bereave them,",["i","that there shall"],"not",["i","be"],"a man",["i","left:"],"yea, woe also to them when I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"depart"],"from them!"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.13","order":"02.29.009.60441"},["b","13"],"Ephraim, as I saw",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Tyrus"],",",["i","is"],"planted in a pleasant place: but Ephraim shall bring forth his children to the murderer."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.14","order":"02.29.009.60442"},["b","14"],"Give them, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": what wilt thou give? give them a miscarrying womb and dry breasts."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.15","order":"02.29.009.60443"},["b","15"],"All their wickedness",["i","is"],"in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Gilgal"],": for there I hated them: for the wickedness of their doings I will drive them out of mine house, I will love them no more: all their princes",["i","are"],"revolters."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.16","order":"02.29.009.60444"},["b","16"],"Ephraim is smitten, their root is dried up, they shall bear no fruit: yea, though they bring forth, yet will I slay",["i","even"],"the beloved",["i","fruit"],"of their womb."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.17","order":"02.29.009.60445"},["b","17"],"My God will cast them away, because they did not hearken unto him: and they shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"wanderers"],"among the nations."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.1a","order":"02.29.009.60446"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/31.16"},"Deut. 31:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/5.3"},"Hosea 5:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.1b","order":"02.29.009.60448"},["b","1b"],["span.small","OR"],"harlot’s hire."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.1c","order":"02.29.009.60450"},["b","1c"],["span.small","OR"],"threshing floor."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.3a","order":"02.29.009.60452"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.7"},"Jer. 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.3b","order":"02.29.009.60454"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/8.13.11-14"},"Hosea 8:13 (11–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.3c","order":"02.29.009.60456"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/4.13"},"Ezek. 4:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.8"},"Dan. 1:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.6a","order":"02.29.009.60458"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"tents."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.7a","order":"02.29.009.60460"},["b","7a"],["span.small","HEB"],"punishment.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.3"},"Isa. 10:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/56.1"},"D&C 56:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.7b","order":"02.29.009.60462"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.3"},"Ezek. 13:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.9a","order":"02.29.009.60464"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/32.7"},"Ex. 32:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.11"},"D&C 38:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.9b","order":"02.29.009.60466"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/19.14.12-30"},"Judg. 19:14 (12–30)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/10.9"},"Hosea 10:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.10a","order":"02.29.009.60468"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/24.2"},"Jer. 24:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.10b","order":"02.29.009.60470"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/25.3.1-3"},"Num. 25:3 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.28"},"Ps. 106:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.10c","order":"02.29.009.60472"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sexual-immorality"},"TG Sexual Immorality"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.12a","order":"02.29.009.60474"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.14"},"1 Sam. 16:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/28.15.15-16"},"28:15 (15–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.18"},"Ezek. 10:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.13a","order":"02.29.009.60476"},["b","13a"],["span.small","IE"],"Tyre."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.15a","order":"02.29.009.60478"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/12.11"},"Hosea 12:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.4"},"Amos 4:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.17a","order":"02.29.009.60480"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."]]}
